  <part id="admin">
    <title>Administrator Guide</title>
    <partintro>
      <para>This part explains how to configure and administer GeoNetwork based applications using
        its web and desktop tools. The tools are subdivided into 2 categories: </para>
      <orderedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Web tools: these are directly accessible from the web interface and allow the user
            to tune almost all aspects of GeoNetwork. </para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
          <para>The GAST tool: this application provides special functions that cannot be executed
            while GeoNetwork is running. It also performs special tasks that are better done in a
            separate tool.</para>
        </listitem>
      </orderedlist>
    </partintro>
